snippet: Johnny Manziel, playing in what may have been his final college game, passed for two touchdowns and ran for another in the second half to lead the Aggies to a win over Duke.
abstract: Johnny Manziel, playing in what may have been his final college game, passes for two touchdowns and runs for another in the second half to lead Texas A&M to 52-48 victory over Duke.
lead_paragraph: Johnny Manziel, playing in what may have been his final college game, passed for two touchdowns and ran for another in the second half to lead the Aggies to a win over Duke.
